No one would do that in the incident, but only her, our bravest shark, was trying to save and protect Coco in this incident. Her action moved me deeply, so I decided to follow and subscribe her channel, always believe one day she will have 1M sub soon.

No doubts that she was one of favorites vtuber in our life.
Anyway, I wish one day Gura will have the 3D mode suit for her character, and keep singing a song for us. Hope she won't having any pressure in her channel after 1M sub.
